Step 2 : Add a URL Route
from django.urls import path
from django.views.generic import TemplateView

urlpatterns = [
    path('about/', TemplateView.as_view(template_name='about.html'), name='about'),
]

Step 3: Add link in the footer 
< a href="{% url 'about' %}" style="color: #fff; margin:  px;">About Us</a>


Final Output::::
About Us page will be displayed as:
. Restaurant history
. Mission statement
. A list of unique selling points
. Clean, well-formatted presentation

         

